		"description": "<p>The coca bush is 7-10 feet tall, with curved branches. It has opaque, narrow, oval leaves which taper at the extremities. It is known for its powerful stimulant and hunger-suppression properties.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Effect.</strong></em> Those who chew the leaves of the coca plant will remove the [[/condition id=frightened]] condition, and they will have advantage on saving throws and checks vs fear or the frightened condition for 1 hour.</p>",
